subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] On PALM

messageBody:
John Cowan skribis:
>
> Ron Cameron scripsit:
>>
>> Speak for yourself. In my dialect the "l" in palm,
>> psalm, calm, balm, etc., is pronounced. :-)
>
> Hmm. What dialect do you speak?

I too pronounce the "l" in these words. I've lived
all my fifty-two years about fifty miles west of
Detroit, Michigan.

--Ph. D.
